{"tid":1067063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵總監：港鐵沒有問題  是供應問題  明天不可能恢復正常","createTime":"2019-03-18T09:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T04:26:27.000Z","uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb7a76a8e6b0520dec62cb69fa2e7e165d8143d","tid":1067063,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T09:35:25.000Z","msg":"港鐵今日（18日）凌晨近3時，在荃灣綫測試新信號系統期間，中環至金鐘站有列車相撞。事件導致荃灣綫金鐘至中環全日暫停，港鐵車務總監劉天成就事件向市民致歉。<br />\n<br />\n大約下午5時，港鐵再度會見傳媒交代事件。港鐵常務總監金澤培表示，經過供應商模擬測試系統情況後，發現系統確實有問題，會發生事故。劉天成指，在未查出意外原因前，所有信號系統測試都會暫停，包括觀塘線的測試。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2564526/org/e5bc467c55ec4030db9070d22656dfcf.jpg/tHvdlJ_0QWFlQGpopNeuv_MEib6Dh858-pa5FfqWuRU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2564526%2Forg%2Fe5bc467c55ec4030db9070d22656dfcf.jpg%2FtHvdlJ_0QWFlQGpopNeuv_MEib6Dh858-pa5FfqWuRU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c8d18767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金澤培表示，供應商將派4至5位專家來港協助調查事件，並會下載電腦運作的涉事經過，研究事故成因。惟牽涉軟件開發程序及系統保障程序，故需時約2至3個月，並在目前階段停止所有新信號系統的列車測試。<br />\n<br />\n金澤培確認，事發時涉事車長有煞停列車，惟火車需要一段距離才能停車，故未能阻止兩列列車相撞。"},{"pid":"d7196fc7b038f065e00181f9692188916230c980","tid":1067063,"uid":212493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗膠唔佑俾咩反應好"},{"pid":"300b8f0818a563b0fa36db23f1c75e0ed3f52f3e","tid":1067063,"uid":81692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"我話ok就ok啦"},{"pid":"da29a1f0e474f0df5cd467611ede488e265effd4","tid":1067063,"uid":98795,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"即係話你班 engine垃圾啦，無你地批個 test plan/spec. 做閪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caff4f8c411dd3d56b4c910615d4aa1e2c45c1d8","tid":1067063,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff38055b10db45cefac60520fafbe65768878551","tid":1067063,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"隻窗跌落街係抺窗條友有問題<br />\n同隻窗都有問題<br />\n唔關大廈管理事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}